<bibRefCitation author="Vaillant, F" editor="Lindner, E" journalOrPublisher="E. Schweizerbart'sche Verlagsbuchhandlung, Stuttgart" pageId="9" pageNumber="158" pagination="207 - 238" title="Psychodidae-Psychodinae." volumeTitle="Die Fliegen der Palearktischen Region" year="1978">Vaillant (1978)</bibRefCitation>
. It also occurs in mainland Spain and in North Africa (
<bibRefCitation author="Vaillant, F" editor="Lindner, E" journalOrPublisher="E. Schweizerbart'sche Verlagsbuchhandlung, Stuttgart" pageId="9" pageNumber="158" pagination="207 - 238" title="Psychodidae-Psychodinae." volumeTitle="Die Fliegen der Palearktischen Region" year="1978">Vaillant 1978</bibRefCitation>
